Prof. NohmNohmz
[[Image:ToughGuyNohmNohmz.JPG|thumb|NohmNohmz' e-image left, the real NohmNohmz right]]

'''Leyland Ohmer''', better known as [[Prof. NohmNohmz]] is a [[weaboo]] [[Internet tough guy]] who frequents a [[faggot|Sonic Adventure 2 Chao board]]. On [[last thursday|22nd Feburary]] [[2008]], he was successfully [[troll|trolled]] by a closet [[furry]] by the name of Tails. His subsequent rage over the [http://tails03.sonicteam.com/bbs/chao_en/index.html CHAO BBS] came to the attention of [[Anonymous]] and resulted in a shitstorm that left the peaceful BBS [[holocaust|forever devastated]].

