[[Image:ChaoRule34.jpg|thumb|Rule 34|Completely inevitable]]

== Chao Trolling ==
: '''''"I think of Tails all day, every day ... his cute face and [[spellcheck|goregous body]] - Tails"'''''
Our story begins with an Anonymous by the name of [[Homosexuality|Tails]] posting on a message board created for the intention of providing advice to [[Sonic CulT|Sonic fans]] in raising their "Chaos" - pronounced "CHOW" as in "CHOW ON COCKS", miniature [[fat]] creatures used as some sort of [[creepy|3D Sonic Tamagotchi]].

It did not take long for the board's [[fursecution|righteous anger]] to kick up, countered with further trolling by Tails.

